               <p>HEPHZIBAH WALTERS. I am the wife of 
               <persName id="t18230115-90-person848">
                  Robert 
                  Walters
               <interp inst="t18230115-90-person848" type="surname" value="Walters"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230115-90-person848" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230115-90-person848" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
